1
00:00:01,740 --> 00:00:05,950
<i>Makoto loses her memories after a nighttime fall among the cherry blossoms raining down.</i>

2
00:00:05,950 --> 00:00:10,970
<i>She searches for her love and herself</i>

3
00:00:10,970 --> 00:00:14,310
<i>with a man's ring as her guide.</i>

4
00:00:14,310 --> 00:00:17,790
<i>As she navigates her amnesia, three men come into her life.</i>

5
00:00:17,790 --> 00:00:20,670
<i>One claims to be her ex,</i>

6
00:00:20,670 --> 00:00:21,950
<i>another her friend,</i>

7
00:00:21,950 --> 00:00:23,840
<i>and another her destiny.</i>

8
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:29,990
<i>With their help, Makoto-chan believes in herself and begins to move forward.</i>

9
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:33,790
<i>However, as her memories slowly return,</i>

10
00:00:33,790 --> 00:00:36,420
<i>Makoto begins to have doubts about these three.</i>

11
00:00:36,420 --> 00:00:37,420
<i>What's wrong?</i>

12
00:00:37,420 --> 00:00:40,580
<i>We hadn't met before I lost my memories, had we?</i>

13
00:00:40,580 --> 00:00:41,650
<i>Why ask?</i>

14
00:00:41,650 --> 00:00:45,920
<i>I'm not really your friend.</i>

15
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:49,040
<i>What secrets do they hold?</i>

16
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:51,960
<i>Who is the man behind the ring?</i>

17
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:55,320
<i>I can't remember whom this ring was for.</i>

18
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:58,530
<i>Given my situation, should I really be falling in love?</i>

19
00:00:58,530 --> 00:01:00,700
<i>But you've already fallen for someone, haven't you?</i>

20
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:05,510
<i>Even while you were with me, wasn‚Äôt he the one on your mind all along?</i>

21
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:10,680
Welcome.
