Sorry, I'm not here to buy flowers.
<i>[Episode 9]</i>

23
00:01:14,340 --> 00:01:16,010
I just wanted to see you.

24
00:01:20,010 --> 00:01:24,390
I was worried since I hadn't heard from you since last time.

25
00:01:24,390 --> 00:01:26,940
Sorry for not getting in touch.

26
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:30,990
- I was having trouble choosing a nice date spot.
- Pardon?

27
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:36,560
You asked me to think of where I'd want to go for our date.

28
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:40,840
But you know me; I never had any hobbies.

29
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:43,560
So I'm kind of stumped.

30
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:49,010
I did consider stuff like going to the movies or a museum, but...

31
00:01:49,010 --> 00:01:54,400
I'd rather spend our time talking to each other, not in silence.

32
00:01:55,750 --> 00:01:58,860
Then I became more stuck.

33
00:01:58,860 --> 00:02:01,000
You put that much thought into it?

34
