Wait, were you joking?

35
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:07,300
No, but you didn‚Äôt have to take it so seriously.

36
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:12,050
I would have preferred if you had contacted me.

37
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:15,110
Sorry.

38
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:19,520
How about we start our day walking around?

39
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:23,860
We can think of places to go as we walk.

40
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:25,230
Sure.

41
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,760
- Oh?
- Yes?

42
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:33,550
Where's your ring on a necklace?

43
00:02:36,420 --> 00:02:40,920
I'm fine without that ring now.

44
