I feel bad for my past self and for the person the ring was meant for.

45
00:02:47,420 --> 00:02:50,460
But the current me doesn‚Äôt need it.

46
00:02:51,730 --> 00:02:53,680
Is that so?

47
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,110
Yes.

48
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,400
I almost forgot.

49
00:03:02,830 --> 00:03:05,000
- Scented candles?
- Yes.

50
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:09,790
I've been wanting to sell scented candles made with dried flowers,

51
00:03:09,790 --> 00:03:15,360
