<i>but please come here when you find them pretty, since it is a flower shop.</i>

93
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:57,380
I see. So you got rejected properly

94
00:05:57,380 --> 00:06:00,890
Good job! You did really well.

95
00:06:00,890 --> 00:06:05,530
Well, personally, I'm happy enough to remain as Ogata's friend.

96
00:06:05,530 --> 00:06:09,210
That was an awesome expression! You looked cooler than ever.

97
00:06:09,210 --> 00:06:12,040
Is that supposed to make me feel better?

98
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,790
But I'll be fine.

99
00:06:13,790 --> 00:06:19,080
I'll continue to be there for her, as a friend.

100
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:24,260
The issue now is what happens if her memories return.

101
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:26,610
I suppose you're hoping they do.

102
00:06:26,610 --> 00:06:28,610
I don't mind either way,

103
00:06:28,610 --> 00:06:35,320
although I'd like her to remember sharing her cup noodles with me.

104
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,780
All right. Let's eat ramen.

105
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:41,550
We don't serve any here so I'll Uber some.

106
00:06:41,550 --> 00:06:42,880
Is that even allowed?

107
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:45,950
No, but I can at least treat you to cup noodles.

108
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:47,690
Please don't tarnish my memories.

109
00:06:47,690 --> 00:06:50,050
"Tarnish"? How rude.

110
00:06:50,050 --> 00:06:56,550
In any case, my priority is seeing Makoto-chan find happiness.

111
00:06:57,310 --> 00:07:01,390
Before she lost her memories, I'd barely spoken a word to her.

112
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:03,830
Is that right?

113
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:08,570
She mistook my room for hers the day she left the hospital.

114
00:07:08,570 --> 00:07:11,380
She was searching her phone for clues of herself,

115
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:15,690
and she couldn't even decide what outfit was "normal" for her.

116
00:07:15,690 --> 00:07:19,560
At first, I hoped she would regain her memories soon.

117
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:22,000
But now, I'm not too certain,

118
00:07:23,230 --> 00:07:28,010
though maybe it's best she remembers, for her safety.

119
00:07:28,010 --> 00:07:29,730
"For her safety"?

120
00:07:29,730 --> 00:07:34,980
The other day, she recalled something about being stalked.

121
00:07:34,980 --> 00:07:36,360
What?

122
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,420
She's safe now.

123
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:44,010
But it would be better if she knew, in case something happens.

124
00:07:44,010 --> 00:07:46,250
A stalker...

125
